This is the software, for the Magic Mirror a gesture controlled web browser - published 
in The MagPi No. 44 April 2016

A mirror with a built in program for displaying a pre set number of web pages.
Navigation is performed by the Pimoroni SkyWriter Hat interface, this is used to move between
web page tabs and scroll up and down through a page. All the pages can be refreshed with a wheel spin gesture.
Finally the system can be shut down with a double tap on the sensor board.

A video of this part of the project can be seen at:-
https://vimeo.com/159712525
